How To Buy $WAI

01

Connect Your Wallet

Connect your MetaMask or other wallet to this website using the widget at the top of the page. From there you can easily buy $WAI tokens using ETH, BNB, MATIC, USDT, or bank card.

02

Fund Your Purchase

Ensure you have either ETH, BNB, MATIC, or USDT in your wallet to swap for $WAI. Deposit crypto into your wallet if you don't. Alternatively, use the Card option.

03

Swap Tokens For $WAI

Go to the buy widget and select the amount of tokens you wish to swap for $WAI. Authorize the transactions in your wallet and make you leave enough ETH, BNB, or MATIC for gas fees.

04

Stake $WAI to Earn $WAI

Once you've bought $WAI tokens, you can immediately put them to work. Click on 'Staking' in the menu and stake your tokens early to take advantage of the extremely high APY!

What is the WienerAI Presale?
The WienerAI Presale allows buyers to secure WienerAI tokens at a drastically lower price than the listing price. There are several stages, each lasting 2 days. At each stage, the price will increase until the presale is over.
